            614,
            589,
            630
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Clark AM and Courtman-Stock J. 1976. The Echinoderms of Southern Africa. British Museum (Natural History): London. pp. 73-74 (277pp.).",
        "bbox": [
            509,
            630,
            836,
            675
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Clark AM and Downey ME. 1992. Starfishes of the Atlantic (Volume 3). Chapman and Hall: London. pp. 202-204 (794pp.).",
        "bbox": [
            509,
            680,
            836,
            724
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Species identification confirmed by Dr C. Mah, Smithsonian, Washington, June 2015.",
        "bbox": [
            509,
            728,
            835,
            759
        ],
