        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Clark AM and Courtman-Stock J. 1976. The Echinoderms of Southern Africa. British Museum (Natural History): London. p. 90 (277pp.).",
        "bbox": [
            509,
            677,
