        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "Clark AM and Downey ME. 1992. Starfishes of the Atlantic (Volume 3). Chapman and Hall: London. pp. 220-222 (794pp.).",
        "bbox": [
